            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">The teacher of Zhu Rong 祝融, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">You Cheng, his appearance is like a monkey, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">he has ears but does not hear. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">he has a mouth but does not cries out (=speak) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">His eyes do not see, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">his feet do not walk; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">when he talks one can feel fear, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en">when he walks one can feel scared. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">I say </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">[...] ??? [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">[...] still. ???? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">I say: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">haughty ??? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">he does not eat it, he does not drink it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">This creature can be mistaken (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en">this kind of animal is not a mouse (?). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en">later eat men and does not shine upon them (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en">if one despises the teacher </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en">one is reputed abandoning [him]. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">Utterly destroyed, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">he makes a piece about it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">Similar to that mouse-like animal, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">he has feet and is dry (?). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">Plunged into his thoughts, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en">he rises high (???) </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
